<br>
It's all good. When I think about the possibilities of SWG I get giddy with excitement. Man, I can't wait. You know, it's Verant, but then again, it's not. None of the SWG devs have ever worked on EQ, and it's an entirely separate team in a different region of the country in their own offices. They work hand in hand with Lucasarts; all Verant/Sony does is manage them. McQuaid was producer of SWG for a brief time, but he's gone gone gone. <br>
<br>
Think about this: EQ was an unknown world, and it's got over 400,000 active accounts. How many do you think SWG is going to have, with the STAR WARS title propelling it. SWG is gonna be the largest MMOG ever if done even remotely well. And I think it's going to be better than remotely good, I think it's going to be superb. This game is going to be huge. <br>
<br>
My prediction: SWG will be the first MMOG to ever break 1 million active players worldwide. <p><b>~Merithel Greenstrider, Elegist of Cotswold, Galahad server~</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uhedges.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hedges</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.gamegen.com/fightgen/features/cammy2.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Shrubgawd</span><br>  Posts: 1073<br> <font color=#333333>(4/24/02 4:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstavernfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=150.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.moirai.net/robbyl/vash.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: MY GOD! This is why SWG will rock!</span><hr size=1> I'd be willing to wait another year if it meant they add in more playable races <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ub0fadeez.showPublicProfile?language=EN>B0faDeez</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 563<br> <font color=#333333>(5/1/02 6:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstavernfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=150.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ...</span><hr size=1> what's SWG <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzennishtinypants.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zennish Tinypants</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1331<br> <fo